'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 64''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 64''',  was the sixty-fourth issue of ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]. ''It was released in [[June]] [[2006]] and covering [[July]] and [[August]] 2006, and contained 100 pages.

